		<title>MiCA Decoded: Why the Regulator Sees Your Compliance Team as a Single Brain</title>
		<link>https://news.bitcoin.com/mica-decoded-why-the-regulator-sees-your-compliance-team-as-a-single-brain/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Guest Author]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 11:30:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Legal]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Compliance]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[legal]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[LegalBison]]></category>
